---
// Problem V6 — Logos flottants + 3 symptômes
---

<section class="py-24" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-16">

      <!-- Gauche : titre + symptômes -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 reveal" style="color: var(--accent);">Les 3 symptômes classiques</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-10 reveal">
          Vous reconnaissez-vous
          <span class="font-serif italic" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);"> là-dedans ?</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-1" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-rose-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #f87171;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 10h16M4 14h8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Dispersion sans vision</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">CRM, LinkedIn, refonte site, agent IA... Tout part en même temps. Rien n'avance vraiment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-2" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #fbbf24;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">L'IA comme gadget</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">ChatGPT testé, quelques prompts, un outil acheté. Rien d'intégré au vrai processus métier.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-3" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #818cf8;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Décisions sans boussole</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Par où commencer ? Quel outil choisir ? Sans cadrage, impossible de décider avec confiance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Droite : logos flottants -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-right">
        <div class="logos-chaos relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 1/1; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, rgba(59,130,246,0.08), transparent 60%), linear-gradient(135deg, #080d1a, #0a1020); border: 1px solid var(--border);">

          <!-- Grille de fond -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>

          <!-- Label -->
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 text-center pointer-events-none" style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); text-transform: uppercase;">Vos outils · sans stratégie</div>

          <!-- Logos flottants -->
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 8%; left: 12%; animation-delay: 0s; --glow: rgba(16,185,129,0.4);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/openai/10b981" alt="ChatGPT" width="44" height="44" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 6%; left: 52%; animation-delay: 0.8s; --glow: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/notion/ffffff" alt="Notion" width="38" height="38" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 5%; right: 10%; animation-delay: 1.6s; --glow: rgba(255,74,0,0.5);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/zapier/ff4a00" alt="Zapier" width="42" height="42" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 30%; left: 5%; animation-delay: 2.2s; --glow: rgba(96,165,250,0.4);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/anthropic/60a5fa" alt="Claude" width="36" height="36" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 28%; left: 38%; animation-delay: 0.4s; --glow: rgba(155,89,182,0.5);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/make/9b59b6" alt="Make" width="40" height="40" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 26%; right: 8%; animation-delay: 1.2s; --glow: rgba(0,196,204,0.4);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/canva/00c4cc" alt="Canva" width="38" height="38" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 54%; left: 18%; animation-delay: 1.8s; --glow: rgba(239,83,80,0.4);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/n8n/ef5350" alt="n8n" width="36" height="36" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 56%; left: 52%; animation-delay: 0.6s; --glow: rgba(66,133,244,0.5);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/googlegemini/4285f4" alt="Gemini" width="40" height="40" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 52%; right: 6%; animation-delay: 2.5s; --glow: rgba(99,102,241,0.4);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/hubspot/ff7a59" alt="HubSpot" width="36" height="36" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 76%; left: 8%; animation-delay: 1.4s; --glow: rgba(16,185,129,0.3);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/airtable/18bfff" alt="Airtable" width="34" height="34" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 78%; left: 44%; animation-delay: 0.2s; --glow: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/googleworkspace/4285f4" alt="Google Workspace" width="36" height="36" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top: 74%; right: 10%; animation-delay: 2.0s; --glow: rgba(255,155,100,0.4);">
            <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/microsoftazure/0078d4" alt="Azure AI" width="34" height="34" />
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Message pivot -->
    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl reveal" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.2);">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-lg font-serif italic leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
          "L'IA n'est pas une solution. C'est un levier — et seulement si le problème est bien posé en amont."
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold" style="color: var(--accent);">C'est exactement là qu'intervient le cadrage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .logo-item {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    animation: logo-float 7s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px -5px var(--glow, rgba(96,165,250,0.3));
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .logo-item:hover {
    transform: scale(1.12) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px -5px var(--glow, rgba(96,165,250,0.5));
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .logo-item img {
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  @keyframes logo-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    25%       { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(2deg); }
    75%       { transform: translateY(6px) rotate(-2deg); }
  }
</style>
